{"tid":948350,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日提醒你：李小龍銅像開售","createTime":"2018-12-20T03:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T04:40:41.000Z","uid":188994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3b80d932fed992f43d595a1ba7c6ce7654aa24b9","tid":948350,"uid":188994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:59:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181220/20572925\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181220%2F20572925&d=WR7F0vbvcweQvB3cyi14pm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ae584acf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181220%2F20572925&h=0844a530\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181220/20572925</a><br />\n<br />\n今年是李小龍逝世45周年，香港文化博物館邀請朱達成製作約30厘米高、相同造型的限量版李小龍銅像，每個銅像均刻有獨立編號，今早10時起在博物館禮品店開售，另接受海外郵購。<br />\n售賣日期：今早10時起<br />\n售價：2,780元<br />\n購買方法：親身到香港文化博物館禮品店購買，海外郵購可電郵至able@soleculture.com查詢。每人每次限購一個<br />\n網址： https://www.heritagemuseum.......ationsouvenir/blstatue.html"},{"pid":"35b738c3608ee5f2a8270da14ed3d1d357545803","tid":948350,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:00:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e301ffe77e1c57141d3cca396e17a24e153c3f3e","tid":948350,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:40:41.000Z","msg":"買返去放神台當神拜咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}